rows.label: qst200709_msg0001
rows.name:
Access beyond this point is restricted
to authorized personnel. I'm sorry, but
I'm going to have to ask you to leave.

rows.label: qst200709_msg0002
rows.name:
Could we make some sort of deal?
Say, through the medium of a
3,000G bribe?

rows.label: qst200709_msg0003
rows.name:
You see, I simply have to get
inside His Majesty's chambers!

rows.label: qst200709_msg0004
rows.name:
That's... Wow. You know trying to bribe
an Imperial official is a crime, right?
And so openly, as well...

rows.label: qst200709_msg0006
rows.name:
Or would you rather get a one-way
guided tour of the castle dungeons?!
